00:47:46,614 --> 00:47:49,152
"It's not me. It's not me," right?

693
00:47:49,325 --> 00:47:53,945
Even though that was not
a reasonable thing to say.

694
00:47:55,956 --> 00:47:59,449
<i>After Lisa was born,
Steve came up three days later.</i>

695
00:47:59,585 --> 00:48:02,293
<i>And we're sitting in a field,
