717
00:49:45,608 --> 00:49:48,476
<i>and she decided
to put me up for adoption.</i>

718
00:49:48,611 --> 00:49:50,318
<i>So, everything was all set</i>

719
00:49:50,446 --> 00:49:53,939
<i>for me to be adopted at birth
