764
00:52:48,666 --> 00:52:53,161
<i>A woman with a baby,
and I was that threatening to them.</i>

765
00:52:53,295 --> 00:52:56,629
<i>"If he'd said," I can't do this,
but let me help</i>

766
00:52:56,757 --> 00:52:59,875
because I can be practical here,"

767
00:53:00,010 --> 00:53:02,002
that would have been...

768
00:53:02,179 --> 00:53:04,762
made for so much.

769
00:53:04,890 --> 00:53:09,100
But it almost seemed that the point
