784
00:54:25,179 --> 00:54:27,045
Does that make sense?

785
00:54:29,016 --> 00:54:32,726
He made up another kind of connection.

786
00:54:39,026 --> 00:54:41,063
You know,
I didn't sleep a wink last night.

787
00:54:41,236 --> 00:54:47,403
There's a version of Steve Jobs
presenting the iPhone

788
00:54:47,576 --> 00:54:52,913
<i>where you can see his own feeling
