877
01:00:12,359 --> 01:00:17,150
OK, so, a monomaniacal commitment
to something

878
01:00:17,280 --> 01:00:19,567
is something
that most people don't have.

879
01:00:20,909 --> 01:00:28,624
<i>And that, like the monk, requires you
