974
01:07:09,901 --> 01:07:11,563
<i>Fred kept going,
"You know, wait a minute,</i>

975
01:07:11,694 --> 01:07:13,276
<i>we got to have a consumer product."</i>

976
01:07:13,404 --> 01:07:15,111
<i>"You guys have to focus
