980
01:07:26,626 --> 01:07:29,414
There you go, right here.
Can you see it?

981
01:07:31,506 --> 01:07:33,964
<i>♪ She comes in colors everywhere</i>

982
01:07:34,092 --> 01:07:37,426
In the world of computers,
