997
01:08:26,394 --> 01:08:28,477
<i>that they thought was impossible.</i>

998
01:08:29,814 --> 01:08:32,727
<i>Steve did create
reality distortion around him.</i>

999
01:08:32,859 --> 01:08:35,021
You know, if he told you
